================================================================================
DISCLAIMER
================================================================================

This software is provided for personal financial management purposes only.
The developers make no warranties about the accuracy, reliability, or security
of this software when used with real financial data.

IMPORTANT SECURITY NOTICES:

1. This software connects to your Bunq bank account in READ-ONLY mode.
   It cannot create transactions or modify your account.

2. Always use this software via VPN for maximum security.
   NEVER expose the dashboard directly to the internet.

3. Store your Bunq API key securely (use Vaultwarden as recommended).
   Never commit API keys or passwords to version control.

4. The session-based authentication implementation is recommended for
   production use over the basic or secure versions.

5. Regular security updates are recommended. Monitor the GitHub repository
   for security announcements and updates.

6. Use at your own risk. The developers are not responsible for any
   financial losses, data breaches, or security incidents resulting from
   the use of this software.

7. This software is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by
   Bunq B.V. or any of its affiliates.

